      <div xml:id="TheLongView"> 
              <interpGrp type="poembox">
                <interp ana="#form" type="freeverse"></interp>
                <interp ana="#tone" type="happy"></interp>
                <interp ana="#topic" type="society"></interp>
              </interpGrp>
             <lg> 
              <l>Some days of days!Some dawning yet to be</l>
          <l>I shall be clothed with immortality!</l> 
          <l>And, in that day, I shall not greatly care</l>
          <l>That Jane split candle grease upon the stair.</l>
          <l>It will not grieve me then, as once it did,</l>
          <l>That careless hands have chipped my teapot lid.</l>
          <l>I groan, being burdened. But in that glad day,</l>
          <l>I shall forget vexations of the way.</l>
          <l>That needs were often great, when means were small,</l>
          <l>Will not perplex me any more at all</l>
          <l>A few short years at most (it may be less),</l>
          <l>I shall forget vexations of the way.</l>
          <l>So, for this day, I lay me at Thy feet.</l>
          <l>O, keep me sweet, my Master!</l>     
          <l>Keep me sweet.</l>     
                 
